1
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,000
Master.

2
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:14,280
Just take me with you.

3
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,540
I am sticking with you.

4
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,400
Didn't I tell you last night?

5
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:20,660
Stop following me.

6
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:21,540
Master.

7
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,280
I promise.

8
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:23,680
I absolutely won't bother you.

9
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,340
Just let me serve by your side.

10
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:26,560
Move.

11
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:27,600
Master.

12
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,280
I...

13
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,680
Why are you still following me?

14
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,140
Master.

15
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,079
This road was built by the government.

16
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:52,040
You go your way.

17
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:52,930
I'll go mine.

18
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,579
How is that following you?

19
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:51,880
Sir,

20
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,880
are you eating or staying the night?

21
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,210
Bring a pot of good wine.

22
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,960
And heat up some vegetables and dried meat.

23
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,560
Okay, please wait a moment.

24
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:05,960
Kid,

25
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,480
go beg somewhere else.

26
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:08,010
Get lost.

27
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,880
Who said I'm a beggar?

28
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:16,040
You.

29
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,200
Bring me your best wine

30
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:20,959
and meat.

31
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,680
Do you have money?

32
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,680
Stop pretending.

33
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,800
Hurry up and get lost.

34
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,200
Don't delay my business.

35
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,980
I have plenty of money.

36
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,600
I failed to recognize your greatness.

37
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,880
Forgive my neglect.

38
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,280
The best wine and meat will be served right away.

39
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,440
Coming right up. Please wait.

40
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,320
Go away.

41
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,480
Just a moment.

42
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,720
Drink.

43
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:37,040
Can I help you?

44
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,460
What are you doing?

45
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,200
Where did these things

46
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:47,840
come from?

47
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:49,960
They're mine.

48
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,600
Yours?

49
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,720
You're so young.

50
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,980
Where did you get so much gold and silver?

51
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,780
My family gave it to me.

52
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,800
From your family?

53
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,240
Look at your outfit.

54
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,680
Do you look like you are from a wealthy family?

55
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:05,480
Recently, wealthy merchants in town were robbed.

56
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,080
Could it be

57
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,740
that you did it?

58
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,090
No, it wasn't me.

59
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,120
Still denying it?

60
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,240
Confiscate the gold and silver.

61
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,640
Escort him back to the government office.

62
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,480
It really wasn't me.

63
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,080
No, no, no.

64
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,650
It really wasn't me.

65
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:20,770
Let me go!

66
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,480
Sir, it really wasn't me.

67
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,360
Let me go!

68
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:24,570
Move!

69
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,130
Who's blocking the way?

70
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,040
It is I,

71
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,200
Gesang.

72
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,159
What proof do you have

73
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,280
that this boy's gold and silver

74
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:49,940
are stolen?

75
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,680
Coming to this wilderness

76
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,280
with so much gold and silver.

77
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,320
If it isn't stolen,

78
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,580
where did it come from?

79
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,250
Besides,

80
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,680
even if there's a mistake,

81
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,120
we will take him back to the office

82
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,680
and find out through interrogation.

83
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,760
You have no right

84
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,300
to point fingers here.

85
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,320
Get lost!

86
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:08,370
Or you'll be charged with obstructing official duties.

87
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,180
Take him back to the yamen.

88
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,680
I'm afraid you corrupt officials

89
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,880
want to embezzle these gold and silver.

90
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,250
Then you'll find a place

91
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,540
to bury this young man,

92
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,480
without anybody

93
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,680
knowing.

94
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,010
How dare you!

95
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,440
How dare you slander an imperial official?

96
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,680
Men, arrest her!

97
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,140
Be careful!

98
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,920
I'll deal with you first.

99
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,380
Master.

100
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:11,720
Today,

101
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,920
there are really a lot of people seeking death.

102
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,400
Attack!

103
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:15,240
Yes.

104
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,720
Divine Taiji,

105
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,200
Heaven and Earth align,

106
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,320
Energy of the Eight Wastelands,

107
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,580
Yin and Yang manifest.

108
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,159
Xun position.

109
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,600
This guy actually knows sorcery.

110
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,400
Just you wait.

111
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,880
When I return to report to the Sitian Tower,

112
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,610
I will have all of you arrested.

113
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,000
Retreat.

114
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,840
Where did this gold and silver come from?

115
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,800
I went to Leilong's stronghold last night

116
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,330
and found a lot of treasure.

117
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:30,280
I left some

118
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,900
for the villagers.

119
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,120
And the rest

120
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:34,760
I kept for myself.

121
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:35,450
Foolish!

122
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,800
If anyone had stayed behind in the mountain,

123
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,200
you would definitely be dead.

124
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,460
There was no one there.

125
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,160
It seems

126
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,740
Leilong took them all down the mountain.

127
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,200
These treasures

128
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,740
must have been stolen by them.

129
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,520
They should be handed over to the authorities,

130
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,720
who will return them to the people following procedures.

131
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:56,020
Listen.

132
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,920
I'll go with you to the county office

133
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,450
to return these treasures,

134
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:03,860
so you won't get a bounty on your head.

135
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,320
What?

136
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,120
You're not going?

137
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:07,580
I'll go.

138
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,730
I will do as you say, Master.

139
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:12,080
But let me make this clear first.

140
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,880
After returning the property,

141
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,610
you must not follow me anymore.

142
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,660
Otherwise,

143
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,400
I won't go easy on you.

144
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:12,200
Why are you following me?

145
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,180
Master.

146
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:18,840
I...

147
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:21,540
I am Gesang.

148
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,440
You are so skilled.

149
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,380
What sect are you from?

150
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:26,940
None of your business.

151
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:30,740
I know what you are.

152
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,080
You were in danger just now,

153
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,080
but you still restrained yourself.

154
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,520
It shows you are not evil.

155
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:38,580
I will spare your life for now.

156
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:40,320
Don't follow me anymore.

157
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,320
He's just like that.

158
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,180
Sister Gesang.

159
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:50,960
I am Feilu.

160
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:51,960
Thank you.

161
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:53,920
By the way,

162
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,600
if you want someone to look after you,

163
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,960
just follow us secretly.

164
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,620
That master is very powerful.

165
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,160
He is an immortal.

166
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:03,770
An immortal?

167
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:06,530
The way he is,

168
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,080
how does he look like an immortal?

169
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:08,720
Let's go.

170
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,300
Coming.

171
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:17,340
Last night,

172
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:20,520
I felt immortal power nearby through the ley lines.

173
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:21,650
I couldn't be wrong.

174
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,360
Did I really meet one?

175
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,480
Sanshan Sect.

176
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,520
A Golden Immortal.

177
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:53,140
Master.

178
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:54,380
Master.

179
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,050
You hunted this?

180
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:05,280
I learned to hunt with the villagers since I was a kid.

181
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:07,010
They all praised my steady aim.

182
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,300
Not bad.

183
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:27,480
You're too kind, Master.

184
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,720
I'll go find some leaves.

185
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:30,780
We can use them as a mattress tonight.

186
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,220
Sister Gesang.

187
00:13:58,920 --> 00:13:59,320
For me?

188
00:13:59,520 --> 00:13:59,960
Yeah.

189
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:02,040
I couldn't just watch you go hungry.

190
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:02,570
Besides,

191
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,450
I owe you one.

192
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:08,100
Thanks.

193
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,320
Thank you.

194
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:12,880
You said

195
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:14,280
he is an immortal.

196
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,770
Have you seen him transform into an immortal?

197
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,280
Sister Gesang,

198
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:20,480
I promised the Master

199
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:22,000
not to tell anyone about this.

200
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:22,440
Plus,

201
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,080
I am

202
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,300
tight-lipped.

203
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:26,520
So stop asking me about it.

204
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,610
So you haven't seen it then.

205
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,880
Of course I have!

206
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:32,080
When he transforms, he glows with golden light,

207
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,880
and holds a five-colored sword.

208
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:40,920
Pretend I didn't say anything.

209
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:41,650
I'm leaving.

210
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:49,040
Then it must be him.

211
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,200
Ping Jie, Qiang Haihui.
